data.description: Fabulous Sun Valley property with amazing location near schools, parks, shopping and entertainment! This bi-level property makes excellent use of space. The lower level features a fully updated kitchen including gorgeous granite countertops, new cabinetry and a dining space with a large buffet counter. It’s perfect for guests to serve themselves during dinner parties or Family gatherings. The color schemes, custom wall treatments and stainless appliances lend a modern feel to the space. Separated from the main living area is the spacious primary bedroom with a custom barn door greeting you into the space and direct access to the back yard. Adjacent to the primary bedroom is the large laundry room with included washer and dryer and large wash sink.  The modern updated 3/4 bathroom is convenient to both the primary bedroom and the main living area. Entering the home through the garage offers a mudroom, excellent for keeping coats and boots off the beautiful hardwood flooring found throughout the home. Upstairs you’ll find a large living room, 3 nice sized bedrooms and a full updated bath. The 28x25 oversized garage provides more than enough space to store your cars & trucks. The nearly 12,000 square foot lot features a fenced back yard with mature trees and an oversized driveway capable of storing boats, campers or other fun stuff!
